FIRSTLY, THANK you for downloading my map!

This map is the only map made with Disco and with a double bridge! There is two secret rooms in the map, one for T and one for CT, good luck finding them ;-)

You are more than welcome to join us at: 217.163.30.167:27015 - [DK] Hoejhus 24/7 |FFA - 100 TICK!|

You can also just join our SteamGroup: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/HoejhusServer

I hope you will Enjoy the map and I hope to see you soon on the server! ;-)

NB! NB! NB!
This is not as big as the old DoubleMix I made. I found out some servers had problems running my map because it was to big. So now it should work. I also fixed some "texture" errors. I decided to delete them so fare, until I'll find out the problem. Enjoy! ;-)

You can still download my old DoubleMix_v1 - Here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/86738
